<h2 id="thumbnails-custom-content">Custom content</h2>
<p>With a bit of extra markup, it's possible to add any kind of HTML content like headings, paragraphs, or buttons into thumbnails.</p>
<div class="thumbnail">
	<img src="{{ src }}" alt="{{ alt }}">
	{{# captionClass }}
  	<div class="caption">
  	{{{ caption }}}
	</div>
	{{/ captionClass }}
</div>

